name: Endemol Digital Media
description: Digital Media Subdivision of Endemol UK
overview:
Endemol UK is at the cutting-edge of cross-platform digital broadcasting and has recently established a dedicated digital board at the heart of the company.

Endemol’s digital credentials and expertise cover content from all of Endemol UK’s portfolio of entertainment brands such as The Million Pound Drop (Channel 4) Big Brother (Channel 4) and Deal Or No Deal (Channel 4); to new online projects like Beat (Bebo); The Gap Year (Bebo); Cell (o2) and the award-winning Kirill (MSN).

Endemol UK develops and manages large entertainment, reality and event based websites for broadcasters, partners and distributors.
